name: Export My Posts to Google Sheet (demo)

customFields.description: Export your posts to Google Drive Spreadsheet.

fields.label: Excel Sheet File Name
fields.tooltip: Enter a file name including the .xlsx extension.

fields.label: Google Drive Folder
fields.tooltip: Select your Google Drive folder where the resulting excel sheet will be uploaded.

fields.label: Email Notification Recipient Address
fields.tooltip: Enter an email address that will receive a notification when the export is finished.
